{"tid":1599482,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發悲劇] 坤哥將會離開樂壇","createTime":"2019-09-28T04:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T15:34:09.000Z","uid":111814,"like":7,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"79c8e34e11786b9a4a1df7601b2660710968b10e","tid":1599482,"uid":111814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T04:08:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20190927/s00009/75e0c60bf5b35348a300f482799e35c1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20190927%2Fs00009%2F75e0c60bf5b35348a300f482799e35c1.jpg&h=b6f7029f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據《明周》報道，「星娛樂」今日出現人事變動，公司高層Tommy Chu將於10月中離職，但他否認跟公司蝕錢有關，只是跟老闆薛嘉麟洽談公司明年發展方向時，出現意見分歧。<br />\n<br />\n另外，據悉吳業坤（坤哥）亦決定離開星娛樂，但跟Tommy離職無關，報道指坤哥今年主力拍劇，加上跟星娛樂已約滿，暫時他不再簽約，坤哥想待明年再發展音樂事業時，才再作決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20190927/1569578845333/%E3%80%90%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E4%B8%BB%E5%8A%9B%E6%8B%8D%E5%8A%87%E3%80%91%E5%82%B3%E5%90%B3%E6%A5%AD%E5%9D%A4%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E3%80%8C%E6%98%9F%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20190927%2F1569578845333%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%258B%258D%25E5%258A%2587%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%2590%25B3%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%259D%25A4%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A%25E9%259B%25A2%25E9%2596%258B%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%2598%259F%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%25E3%2580%258D&d=%2F9qUFN9YWCJnPZyZgWzOjytC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=9491f4db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20190927%2F1569578845333%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%258A%259B%25E6%258B%258D%25E5%258A%2587%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%2590%25B3%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%259D%25A4%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A%25E9%259B%25A2%25E9%2596%258B%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%2598%25